-
-### 5. Better interrupt discipline
-
-Without a shared signaling layer, everything urgent becomes either a hard interrupt or a hidden log line.
-
-Connectivity should provide a graded path:
-
-- queued note
-- attention raise
-- escalation required
-- immediate interrupt
-
-### 6. Cleaner synthesis inputs
-
-Synthesis should consume compact, typed signals and linked evidence rather than sprawling internal chat. That gives the coordinator a better chance of producing one coherent assistant answer with fewer contradictory fragments.
-
